e rate, the\nintrinsic $m$. While source classes show composite behavior, the majority of BL\nLac objects favor $m=2$, indicating a synchrotron self-Compton origin for the\n$\\gamma$-rays. No preference for either $m$ is found in flat spectrum radio\nquasars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 May 2019 18:00:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-31"}
