 conditions, deterministic entanglement\nbetween distant individual spins and matter-wave interferometry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 May 2019 21:13:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Nov 2019 17:05:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
